(415, 104, 'content_blocks_0_content_block', '<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    At Capital Street Law, we understand the complexities and challenges individuals and families face when navigating the Canadian immigration process. Our experienced immigration law lawyers are dedicated to providing comprehensive legal services to clients seeking assistance with immigration matters. \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    We are committed to helping you achieve your immigration goals and guiding you through every step of the process.\r\n</p>                            \r\n\r\n<div class=\"service-detials-step-3\">\r\n    <div class=\"row g-5 align-items-center\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12 mb_md--20 mb_sm--20\">\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Express Entry</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Refugee Applications</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Provincial Nominee Programs</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Atlantic Immigration Program</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Rural and Northern Immigration Pilot</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Temporary resident to Permanent Resident</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Economic Mobility Pathways</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Francophone Immigration</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Humanitarian and Compassionate Grounds Applications</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12 mb_md--20 mb_sm--20\">\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Spousal Sponsorship</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Family Sponsorship</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Quebec Selected Skilled Worker</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Caregiver</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Labour Market Impact Assessments</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Self-Employed Categories</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Start-up Visa Program</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Appeals and Judicial Reviews</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                <span>Permanent Resident Pathway for Hong Kong Residents</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>    \r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"disc mt--30\">\r\n    At Capital Street Law, we are committed to providing personalized attention, clear guidance, and effective representation in all Canadian immigration matters. Our team stays up-to-date with the ever-changing immigration laws and regulations to ensure that you receive the most accurate and reliable advice.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc mt--30\">\r\n    Contact us today to schedule a consultation with one of our experienced immigration lawyers. We are here to listen, understand your unique circumstances, and provide you with effective legal solutions tailored to your specific immigration needs in Ontario, Canada.\r\n</p>'),
