(495, 123, 'content_blocks_0_content_block', '<div class=\"title-area\">\r\n    <span class=\"pre-title\">\r\n        Barrister & Solicitor\r\n    </span>\r\n    <h3 class=\"title animated fadeIn\">\r\n        Michael Mangal\r\n    </h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Michael is a Barrister and Solicitor working at Capital Street Law. He obtained his Law Degree from the University of Leicester and is currently licensed by the Law Society of Ontario.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Michael has a passion for Civil Litigation with experience in various types of litigation such as real estate or construction disputes and insurance related disputes. Michael has well-rounded legal experience which also allows him to provide a variety of other services offered by Capital Street Law.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Michael has a desire to bring cost-effective and timely solutions to his clients, depending on the complexity of individual legal matters. Michael helps clients understand the various options available to them in navigating the complex legal system, while advising them on the best steps to move their case forward.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Michael enjoys finding ways to bring cases to the desired resolution for his clients.\r\n</p>'),
