(502, 124, 'content_blocks_0_content_block', '<div class=\"title-area\">\r\n    <span class=\"pre-title\">\r\n        Student at Law\r\n    </span>\r\n    <h3 class=\"title animated fadeIn\">\r\n        Raj Barad\r\n    </h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Raj is a dedicated and ambitious Student at Law at Capital Street Law, currently pursuing their Juris Doctor degree at Osgoode Hall Law School. With a strong academic background in both law and computer engineering, Raj brings a unique perspective to the practice of law, combining legal expertise with technical knowledge.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Prior to pursuing a legal career, Raj obtained a degree in Computer Engineering from Ryerson University. This dual background in law and computer engineering enables him to navigate complex legal issues with a deep understanding of the technical aspects involved.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    As a Summer Law Student at Capital Street Law, Raj has gained practical legal experience under the guidance of our experienced attorneys. He has keen interest in various areas of law, including civil litigation, corporate/commercial law, intellectual property law, and technology law and a genuine passion for the legal implications of emerging technologies, such as cybersecurity, data privacy, and artificial intelligence.\r\n</p>'),
